    },
    {
        "contravallation": "Contravallation"
    },
    {
        ". After a few skirmishes, disease struck the Roman army while supplies in Agrigentum were running low, and both sides saw an open battle as preferable to the current situation. Although the Romans won a clear victory over the Carthaginian relief force at the ": null
